0research%20offers%20a%20look%20at%20how%20some%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20actually%20using%20the%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%2C%20published%20October%208%2C%20come%20from%20the%20Mozilla%20Foundation%20and%20think-tank%20the%20Berggruen%20Institute.%20They%20offer%20a%20rare%20snapshot%2C%20albeit%20based%20on%20a%20limited%20sample%20size%2C%20of%20how%20people%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-investors-ai-hollywood-pitch-decks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHollywood%20are%20using%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20came%20out%20of%20discussions%20with%20174%20people%20working%20in%20creative%20fields%20over%20three%20months%20in%20early%202025.%20The%20largest%20group%20(43%25)%20consisted%20of%20TV%20and%20film%20producers%2C%20directors%2C%20and%20similar%20professionals.%20Others%20represented%20music%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-advice-ai-artist-creative-hollywood-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechnology%20roles%20in%20Hollywood%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20popular%20use%20(19.35%25)%20was%20performing%20tasks%20such%20as%20brainstorming%20ideas%20and%20receiving%20feedback%20on%20story%20concepts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20producer%20said%20in%20the%20report%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20being%20able%20to%20bounce%20ideas%20off%20the%20AI%20like%20I%20do%20my%20other%20writer%20colleagues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feed%20it%20my%20ideas%20and%20it%20generates%20a%20version%20that%20is%20more%20digestible%20and%20concrete%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20prominent%20applications%20of%20AI%20were%20using%20it%20to%20gain%20efficiency%20(17.74%25)%20and%20having%20it%20help%20with%20research-related%20work%20(11.29%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20helps%20me%20summarize%20and%20think%20quickly.%20It's%20definitely%20offloaded%20some%20of%20my%20creative%20thinking%20by%20breaking%20through%20writer's%20block%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20study%20participant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20described%20using%20AI%20to%20speed%20up%20research%2C%20make%20presentations%2C%20clean%20up%20texts%20and%20translations%2C%20and%20generate%20reference%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%208%25%20said%20they%20used%20AI%20in%20every%20step%20of%20their%20creative%20process%2C%20from%20organizing%20their%20workflow%20and%20schedule%20to%20answering%20emails%20and%20writing%20scripts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20a%20substantial%20share%20(19.35%25)%20reported%20that%20AI%20had%20a%20minimal%20effect%20on%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20research%20found%20people%20working%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20business%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0in%20TV%20and%20film%20%E2%80%94%20lag%20their%20tech%20colleagues%20in%20using%20AI.%20More%20than%2081%25%20of%20respondents%20working%20in%20tech%20roles%20said%20they%20used%20AI%2C%20about%20double%20the%20number%20of%20people%20in%20film%2C%20TV%2C%20music%2C%20and%20other%20areas.%20(Tech%20people%20in%20this%20case%20were%20AI%20and%20tech%20builders%2C%20engineers%2C%20technologists%2C%20and%20others.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FdOqSu%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Stacked%20Bars%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FdOqSu%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20Hollywood%2C%20the%20major%20studios%20are%20utilizing%20AI%20to%20different%20degrees%20as%20they%20strive%20to%20do%20more%20with%20less%20and%20catch%20up%20to%20the%20tech%20giants.%20AI%20startups%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoonvalley-raises-84-million-ai-hollywood-tool-studios-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERu