as%20so%20far%20retrofitted%202%2C000%20of%20these%20guns%20for%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20inventor%20John%20Moses%20Browning%20designed%20the%20belt-fed%20heavy%20machine%20gun%20in%201921.%20By%201945%2C%20the%20US%20had%20produced%20and%20distributed%20over%202%20million%20M2s%20among%20Allied%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFN%20Browning%20became%20NATO's%20main%20global%20producer%20of%20the%20M2%20in%20the%201950s%2C%20and%20over%2090%20countries%20still%20use%20the%20heavy%20machine%20gun%20in%20their%20modern%20militaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20M2%20is%20a%20common%20infantry%20weapon%20that%20fires%20while%20mounted%20on%20a%20tripod.%20From%20a%20fixed%20position%2C%20it%20can%20bring%20enemy%20troops%20and%20light%20vehicles%20under%20withering%20.50%20caliber%20fire%20%E2%80%94%20up%20to%20roughly%20600%20rounds%20per%20minute%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20accurate%20against%20targets%20a%20mile%20away.%20Ukraine%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-m2-browning-gun-weapon-choice-ukraine-ai-fighting-robots-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexperimented%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20ground%20robots%20that%20carry%20the%20M2.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222447%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20M2%20Browning%20is%20laid%20out%20on%20snow.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e64a355dbc4fd10daa680f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221538%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThough%20it's%20been%20repeatedly%20upgraded%20and%20improved%2C%20the%20M2%20has%20been%20around%20for%20over%20100%20years.%3Cp%3EFN%20Browning%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDe%20Harenne%20declined%20to%20say%20how%20many%20M2s%20and%20other%20machine%20guns%20the%20Belgian%20group%20is%20producing%20and%20refurbishing%2C%20but%20said%20it%20is%20in%20the%20thousands%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5b4d773-82a9-48c3-a1b2-44ec3fed95ef%5C%22%3EThe%20race%20to%20rearm%20after%20the%20Cold%20War%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFN%20Browning%20reported%20turnover%20of%201.3%20billion%20euros%2C%20or%20%241.5%20billion%2C%20in%202024%2C%20though%20this%20was%20after%20it%20combined%20revenues%20with%20Sofisport%2C%20a%20Paris-based%20ammo%20producer%20that%20it%20purchased%20this%20year.%20FN%20Browning%20reported%20annual%20revenues%20of%20908%20million%20euros%20in%202023%2C%20down%205%25%20from%20956%20million%20euros%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDe%20Harenne%20said%20annual%20turnover%20was%20static%20despite%20the%20surge%20in%20machine-gun%20demand%20due%20to%20lower%20sales%20in%20FN%20Browning's%20sport%20shooting%20division%2C%20which%20is%20coming%20off%20a%20boom%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20declined%20to%20say%20how%20much%20the%20firm%20expects%20demand%20for%20machine%20guns%20to%20increase%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20But%20he%20said%20its%20factory%20campus%20in%20Herstal%20currently%20employs%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eabout%201%2C600%20people%20and%20is%20seeking%20to%20recruit%20another%20100%20mechanics%2C%20machinists%2C%20and%20other%20staff%20for%20ammo%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20FN%20Browning%20executive%20holds%20the%20FN%20Evolys.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e6475f1c1f80efbec52474%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20FN%20Browning%20executive%20holds%20the%20FN%20Evolys%2C%20a%20new%20ultralight%20machine%20gun%20that%20the%20company%20is%20selling%20to%20Belgium%20and%20France.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Loh%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20drone%20war%20is%20shaping%20market%20demand%20in%20other%20ways%3B%20de%20Harenne%20said%20governments%20have%20been%20asking%20more%20about%20firearms%20for%20countering%20uncrewed%20aerial%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKyiv's%20troops%2C%20for%20example%2C%20frequently%20use