%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20utility%20customer%20in%20the%20US%2C%20you've%20likely%20seen%20your%20rates%20go%20up%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%20in%20at%20least%2041%20states%20and%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20are%20experiencing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-bills-rise-13-states-because-big-tech-data-centers-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincreased%20electric%20and%20natural%20gas%20bills%20%3C%2Fa%3Enow%20or%20will%20see%20increases%20in%202026%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanprogress.org%2Farticle%2Fresidents-in-at-least-41-states-and-washington-d-c-are-facing-increased-electric-and-natural-gas-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECosts%20are%20rising%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-operators-concern-power-constraints-price-demand-rise-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20data%20center%20development%3C%2Fa%3E%20boom%20and%20the%20resulting%20strain%20it%20has%20placed%20on%20the%20country's%20aging%20electric%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%20is%20that%2C%20depending%20on%20which%20state%20you%20live%20in%20and%20your%20electricity%20provider%2C%20you%20might%20be%20able%20to%20lower%20your%20bill%20through%20energy%20conservation.%20The%20bad%20news%20is%20that%20simple%20steps%20such%20as%20unplugging%20devices%20and%20turning%20off%20the%20lights%20when%20exiting%20a%20room%20are%20ultimately%20no%20match%20for%20the%20pace%20of%20rising%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20centers%20accounted%20for%204.4%25%20of%20electricity%20consumption%20in%20the%20US%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fescholarship.org%2Fuc%2Fitem%2F32d6m0d1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Lawrence%20Berkeley%20National%20Laboratory.%20That%20amount%20is%20expected%20to%20triple%20by%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUtilities%20across%20the%20country%20are%20predicting%20an%20additional%2060%20gigawatts%20of%20new%20demand%20from%20data%20centers%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade.%20That's%20enough%20electricity%20to%20power%20six%20major%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20utilities%20are%20planning%20multibillion-dollar%20infrastructure%20projects%20to%20meet%20the%20enormous%20demand%20expected%20to%20come%20from%20AI.%20Existing%20regulations%20will%20allow%20much%20of%20those%20costs%20to%20be%20recovered%20from%20a%20utility's%20entire%20customer%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20regulators%20in%20Louisiana%20approved%20Entergy's%20plans%20to%20spend%20%245%20billion%20on%20three%20new%20natural%20gas%20plants%20needed%20to%20serve%20a%20massive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-data-center-louisiana-5b-ratepayers-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20data%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state.%20Consumer%20advocacy%20groups%20opposed%20the%20plan%2C%20arguing%20that%20average%20ratepayers%20would%20ultimately%20bear%20the%20cost%20for%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20companies.%20Similar%20battles%20are%20unfolding%20before%20utility%20regulators%20in%20states%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20creating%20tremendous%20stress%20for%20a%20huge%20segment%20of%20the%20population%20that%20struggles%20to%20pay%20those%20bills%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Conn%2C%20head%20of%20business%20development%20and%20policy%20at%20Exceleron%2C%20an%20energy%20management%20software%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250d2ce71-17fe-4f47-863d-ea1ff1a6fb05%5C%22%3EEnergy%20and%20cost-saving%20tactics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20ever%20reviewed%20your%20energy%20bill%2C%20you%20may%20have%20noticed%20that%20many%20line%20items%20factor%20into%20a%20monthly%20total.%20While%20the%20amount%20of%20energy%20you%20use%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20part%20of%20the%20bill%2C%20utilities%20often%20tack%20on%20charges%20and%20service%20fees%20that%20don't%20have%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20individual%20consumption.%20Data%20centers%20are%20driving%20up%20the%20price%20of%20those%20additional%20charges%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20electricity%2C%20making%20the%20energy%20you%20do%20consume%20more%20costly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3A%20If%20you're%20a%20customer%20of%20a%20utility%20that%20also%20serves%20data%20centers%2C%20your%20bill%20is%20probably%20going%20to%20rise%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20energy%20you%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20of%20those%20things%20where%20consumers%20are%20fighting%20against%20an%20800-pound%20gorilla%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Larry%20Paulhus%2C%20head%20of%20electric%20consulting%20at%20RINA%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20say%20that%20despite%20rising%20costs%2C%20there%20are%20steps%20consumers%20can%20take%20to%20make%20energy%20bills%20more%20manageable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArbor%20is%20part%20of%20an%20emerging%20class%20of%20new%20startups%20aiming%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUtility%20customers%20who%20live%20in%20one%20of%20the%2014%20states%20with%20a%20deregulated%20energy%20market%20can%20use%20Arbor's%20free%20app%20to%20find%20a%20different%20energy%20provider.%20Switching%20providers%20could%20shave%2010%25%20to%2020%25%20off%20monthly%20utility%20bills%2C%20said%20Owen%20Quinlan%2C%20Arbor's%20head%20of%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExceleron%20is%20another%20one.%20The%20company%20offers%20prepay%20programs%20for%2075%20utilities%2C%20including%20major%20providers%20like%20Georgia%20Power%20and%20Salt%20River%20Project%20in%20Arizona.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrepay%20programs%20allow%20utility%20customers%20to%20pay%20their%20bills%20in%20advance%2C%20making%20them%20eligible%20for%20refunds%20later%20on%20if%20they%20consume%20less%20energy%20than%20they%20originally%20paid%20for.%20With%20Exceleron's%20software%2C%20customers%20can%20track%20how%20their%20daily%20energy%20consumption%20affects%20their%20bills%2C%20and%20adjust%20habits%20accordingly%20to%20lower%20the%20amount%20of%20their%20monthly%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20know%20exactly%20how%20much%20money%20programs%20like%20these%20can%20save%20customers.%20There%20are%20many%20line%20items%20on%20an%20electric%20bill%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0such%20as%20costs%20for%20new%20transmission%20lines%20%E2%80%94%20that%20are%20out%20of%20an%20individual%20customer's%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReducing%20a%20home's%20energy%20consumption%20by%2010%25%20likely%20won't%20equate%20to%20a%2010%25%20lower%20bill%2C%20said%20Exceleron's%20Conn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20less%20than%20that%2C%20but%20every%20little%20bit%20helps%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENatural%20gas%20prices%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eia.gov%2Foutlooks%2Fsteo%2Farchives%2FJun25.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E%20right%20now%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%20Energy%20Information%20Administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurbing%20reliance%20on%20gas%20fuel%20can%20help%20lower%20energy%20bills%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20said%20Cooper%20Marcus%2C%20founder%20of%20QuitCarbon%2C%20who%20advises%20homeowners%20on%20energy%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReplacing%20a%20gas%20boiler%20with%20an%20electric%20heat%20pump%20and%20installing%20solar%20panels%20on%20a%20home's%20roof%20can%20lead%20to%20significant%20long-term%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20not%20things%20that%20people%20do%20at%20once%20overnight%2C%20but%20that's%20okay%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marcus.%20%26quot%3BHomes%20last%20for%20decades.%20Our%20investment%20horizons%20should%20be%20decades.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20struggling%20to%20manage%20higher%20rates%20now%2C%20long-term%20solutions%20don't%20offer%20much%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20understandable%20that%20people%20want%20some%20control%20over%20their%20expenses%2C%20and%20there%20are%20things%20that%20people%20can%20do%20to%20bring%20down%20those%20bills.%20It's%20just%20not%20realistic%20for%20so%20many%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sylvie%20Ashford%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20The%20Utility%20Reform%20Network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAshford%20noted%20that%20in%20California%2C%20where%20TURN%20is%20based%2C%2040%25%20of%20the%20population%20are%20renters%20who%20can't%20install%20solar%20panels%20to%20reduce%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETURN%20is%20lobbying%20for%20utilities%20in%20the%20state%20to%20have%20spending%20caps%20tied%20to%20inflation%2C%20among%20other%20initiatives%20aimed%20at%20lowering%20consumer%20electricity%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLegislators%20are%20paying%20attention%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20are%20reporting%20that%20the%20number%20one%20issue%20their%20constituents%20call%20them%20about%20is%20their%20rising%20utility%20bills%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenergy-conservation-hacks-data-center-costs-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759933836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e58ab35dbc4fd10daa621e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenergy-conservation-hacks-data-center-costs-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Data%20centers%20are%20driving%20up%20consumers'%20electricity%20costs%2C%20but%20experts%20say%20energy%20conservation%20hacks%20won't%20lower%20bills%20much.%20Here's%20what%20to%20do%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ellen%20Thomas)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fenergy-conservation-hacks-data-center-cost