0discipline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%222%20grey%20fighter%20jets%20in%20the%20sky%20over%20some%20land%20and%20some%20sea%2C%20with%20one%20banking%20to%20its%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e504f45dbc4fd10daa50ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EF-16s%20from%20the%20Romanian%20Air%20Force%20and%20the%20Portuguese%20Air%20Force%20participating%20in%20NATO's%20Baltic%20Air%20Policing%20Mission%20over%20the%20Baltic%20Sea.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMindaugas%20Kulbis%2C%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20pilots%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20launch%20the%20aircraft%20to%20intercept%20an%20inbound%20bogey%2C%20a%20potential%20threat%2C%20on%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Venable%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20when%20you're%20executing%20the%20intercept%2C%20you%20want%20to%20do%20that%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20to%20cross%20any%20lines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20you%20also%20don't%20want%20to%20put%20you%20or%20your%20wingman%20at%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20instructions%20from%20militaries%20and%20NATO%20are%20clear%2C%20it's%20%26quot%3Bnot%20an%20issue.%26quot%3B%20Pilots%2C%20typically%2C%20know%20the%20rules%20of%20engagement%20and%20authority%20they%20have%20been%20given%2C%20and%20if%20in%20some%20situation%2C%20they%20were%20given%20the%20authority%20to%20shoot%20down%20jets%2C%20they%20would%2C%20likewise%2C%20understand%20%26quot%3Bit's%20their%20responsibility%20to%20do%20just%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pressure%20on%20those%20pilots%20is%20really%20delineated%20by%20the%20rules%20of%20engagement%20and%20the%20special%20instructions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20is%20confident%20Western%20pilots%20are%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20do%20their%20best%20to%20avoid%20conflict%20wherever%20they%20can%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20engage%20in%20unnecessary%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGerman%20Defense%20Minister%20Boris%20Pistorius%20notably%20said%20this%20week%20that%20while%20his%20country%20needs%20more%20anti-drone%20defenses%2C%20it%20must%20be%20careful%20not%20to%20fall%20into%20%26quot%3BPutin's%20escalation%20trap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d5e4f16-a21d-448a-93fa-8c484b586343%5C%22%3EReacting%20to%20gray%20zone%20aggression%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20recent%20incursions%20into%20NATO%20airspace%20come%20as%20many%20European%20countries%20also%20report%20a%20spate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdenmark-said-russia-pointed-weaponry-at-its-helicopters-naval-ships-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20sabotage%20actions%20and%20assassination%20efforts%2C%20with%20officials%20calling%20it%20a%20Russian%20%26quot%3Bshadow%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20at%20war%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20at%20peace%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20NATO%20chief%20Mark%20Rutte%20said%20this%20year.%20Responding%20to%20gray%20zone%20aggression%20is%20complicated%2C%20as%20it%20falls%20below%20the%20threshold%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERutte%20said%20last%20month%20that%20decisions%20over%20whether%20to%20fire%20on%20intruding%20aircraft%20are%20%26quot%3Btaken%20in%20real%20time%2C%20are%20always%20based%20on%20available%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20the%20threat%20the%20aircraft%20poses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20NATO%20will%20always%20react%20proportionately%20and%20act%20if%20necessary%20to%20protect%20people%2C%20cities%2C%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20always%20mean%20shooting%20down%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20secretary-general%20commended%20the%20Italian%20F-35s%20and%20Swedish%20and%20Finnish%20jets%20that%20responded%20in%20Estonia%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Dutch%20F-35s%2C%20Polish%20F-16s%2C%20and%20German%20air%20defenses%20that%20responded%20to%20drones%20over%20Poland.%20The%20drones%20were%20shot%20down.%20The%20encroaching%20MiGs%20were%20not%2C%20and%20he%20said%20that%20was%20the%20right%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20pilots%20are%20doing%20precisely%20what%20they%20are%20trained%20to%20do%20when%20there's%20a%20potential%20risk%20of%20incursion.%20This%20is%20what%20we%20plan%20for.%20What%20we%20train%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20works.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20NATO%20is%20troubled%20by%20Russian%20aggression%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20if%20Russia%20wants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-doesnt-want-nato-war-russia-would-lose-quickly-uk-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewar%20with%20the%20alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20bring%20tremendous%20airpower%20and%20more%20to%20a%20fight%2C%20but%20NATO%20isn't%20banking%20on%20what%20it%20has%20today%20being%20sufficient%20deterrence%2C%20especially%20as%20Russia%20fields%20new%20capabilities%20like%20massed%20drones%20paired%20with%20missiles%20that%20allies%20aren't%20yet%20ready%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20incursions%20are%20a%20clear%20wake-up%20call%20that%20the%20West%20lacks%20enough%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20layered%20air%20defenses%20that%20the%20Ukrainians%20have%20proved%20are%20key%20against%20Russia.%20That%20NATO%20responded%20to%20Russian%20drones%20with%20its%20most%20advanced%20jets%20illustrates%20that%20there%20are%20gaps%20in%20NATO%20defenses%20that%20Russia%20could%20exploit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20new%20investments%20and%20innovations%20are%20being%20directed%20at%20closing%20them%20before%20it's%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-air-policing-riskier-f-35-gripens-f-16-front-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759930249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%